# Product Price Monitoring — PRD v1

Ignore the workspace folder name. This product is **Product Price Monitoring**: a catalog of products with public search and admin-managed pricing/inventory.

## Actors

- **Guest:** Search and browse products; view public details only. No write access.
- **Admin:** Single seeded account (via `DatabaseSeeder`). Must log in to create, update, soft-delete, and restore products. Sees `purchase_price`.

## Domain — Product

| Field | Rules |
|-------|--------|
| `name` | Required |
| `description` | Nullable text |
| `quantity` | Integer ≥ 0 |
| `categories` | Many-to-many (`categories` + `category_product`) |
| `purchase_price` | Decimal; **admin-only** — never expose on public pages |
| `selling_price` | Decimal; public |
| `status` | Enum: `available` \| `unavailable` \| `discontinued` |
| Soft delete | `deleted_at`; soft-deleted products hidden from guests |

## Public landing (`/`)

- Search-first discovery: query by name/description; optional category filter
- Result list + detail: name, description, quantity/availability, categories, selling price, status
- Availability should be clear from `quantity` + `status`
- Guests cannot mutate data

## Admin (auth-gated)

- Login / logout (minimal session auth; no public registration)
- Product CRUD + soft delete / restore
- Category management enough to assign categories on products
- Full field access including `purchase_price`

## Out of scope (v1)

Multi-user roles, public registration, price history charts, inventory transactions, payments, multi-tenant, mobile API.

## Recommended next (v1.x)

- Price history / change log when purchase or selling price updates
- Admin margin display (`selling_price - purchase_price`)
- Low-stock threshold / badge when quantity is below N
- Indexed or full-text search as the catalog grows
- Policies/gates even with one admin (ready for more admins)
- SEO-friendly public detail URLs (`/products/{slug}`)
- Pagination and empty states on search results
